Additional HCP terraform features : 

Health assessments : 
------------------
Terraform can automatically run health assessments on your workspaces once every 24hrs or so.
Checks for Drift detection.

Workspaces often depends on each other

Run triggers : 

HCP Terraform  > networking workspace >managed infra   
                    plan-> apply
                         |
                      Run Triggers
                      Queue a run
                      Firewall workspace


Benefits of run triggers :
- Run triggers let u connect a workspace to one or more source workspaces.
- HCP terraform automatically queues a run in the connected downstream workspace.
- Each workspace can connect to up to 20 source workspaces.
- Run triggers fires on successful applies in source workspaces and that they enable workspace-to-workspace automation.

Tracking Work  :
----------------
- As your org scales, you will have hundreds of workspaces.
- Some might need updates, version, upgrades and fixes.
- you need the ability to add to-do items you can attach to workspaces.

TRACKING WORK WITH CHANGE REQUESTS(basically notes or tickets) : 
- Change requests are actionable "todo" items u can attach to workspaces.
- u add the messages directly from the explorer and they get tracked for each workspace.
- Teams can be notified when new change requests are created on their workspaces.
- Available in standard and premium editions.















